<P>Easy, but not convenient if the illusion doesn't last very long.&nbsp; Imagine if they gave us the 3+ minute boon of garou illusion?&nbsp; You'd have to re-illusion and re-shrink your pet every 3 minutes or so.&nbsp;</P>
